{"tid":1089991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"儲錢有乜用。每月儲20k都追唔到樓價","createTime":"2019-04-03T07:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T09:19:35.000Z","uid":70256,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbaa313172f10a7497aee76b672711b708d51f0","tid":1089991,"uid":70256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n<br />\n上年既今日，我下定決心每個月儲2萬目標係400萬大西北上車盤。<br />\n然後呢一年旅行又唔敢去，朋友女友開始有微言，家用唔敢加，老母開始餐餐煮罐頭，衫褲鞋襪唔敢買多二件，腦細問我去唔去sogo感謝日。<br />\n<br />\n一年過後，加埋月供股票既斬獲，終於儲到30萬，距離成功上車走前一大步。<br />\n<br />\n心諗 呢一年黎既辛苦無都白費到，我買左今年第一杯starbuff奬勵自己然後去地產鋪行返個圈，探下自己層樓 。<br />\n<br />\n突然發現，本來400萬既樓依家要463萬。我沖入去問地產點解貴左63萬，仲要無得做9成按。個地產妹乜都無講，send左條link比我<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2225203/香港樓價指數按年升15.7%25%20奪全球最高\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2225203%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8715.7%2525%2520%E5%A5%AA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e04303da\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2225203/香港樓價指數按年升15.7%25%20奪全球最高</a><br />\n<br />\n今日我決定唔再曬時間儲錢，應該係最年輕既時候享受。"},{"pid":"76cfe35a0c8febe2774c1a750f06bdcee2860235","tid":1089991,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"740e6b4e193553a2a33a10077981768e578ddfce","tid":1089991,"uid":180326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"儲黎積穀防飢（有急事/比人炒）<br />\n 唔一定買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760f6e9d8b157ae2725466b8dba13b5d1fead224","tid":1089991,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"儲到60歲就可以買到<br />\n買完2年番天家"},{"pid":"5a2c4845f4362ccda23d5cd45c8a2e5b73a5bdd1","tid":1089991,"uid":177288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"今日嘅大西北變左離島<br />\n梅窩樓300萬都有交易<br />\n<br />\n上車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89591b781ad868df5c1d1254be3085ac44303b9f","tid":1089991,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"儲埋去第二個國家退休都好阿，<br />\n點都要儲既，有咩病起馬都頂到下"},{"pid":"fb877fc34220330a70c50dec5523829b769b4c7c","tid":1089991,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"儲一年錢就想買樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}